doc.after: The majority of RNZAF personnel served with RAF units six RNZAF Article XV squadrons which were RNZAF units attached to RAF formations and the Fleet Air Arm in Europe the Mediterranean South East Asia and other theatres Commonwealth personnel under RAF operational control were pooled for operational practicality and many RNZAF airmen also served with Royal Australian Air Force or Royal Canadian Air Force Article XV squadrons
